          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TELES",
                "CSICR",
                "SIBAR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Proton recoil. The neutron angular",
                "distribution was measured with a proton recoil",
                "telescope counter. In this counter protons are",
                "scattered out of a polyethylene foil 43 mg/cm3",
                "thick and detected by a CsI crystal a transmission",
                "Au-Si surface barrier detector 300 um thick is",
                "inserted between foil and crystal. To reduce the",
                "background the pulse height spectrum of the CsI",
                "crystal is gated by the coincidence pulse of two",
                "counters. In this was the background counting rate",
                "measured without the polythene foil was only about 3%",
                "of the counting rate obtained with the foil in",
                "position. At a deuteron energy of 1 MeV the neutrons",
                "were monitored by the associated alpha particle",
                "method, and at deuteron of 1.5 and 2 MeV by two Au-Si",
                "surface barrier detectors. The monitors were mounted",
                "12 cm from the target at an angle of 140 degr."
              ]
            }
          ],
